    <h1>SHREE Collective — 3-Person Team Walkthrough &amp; Viva Guide</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Project:</strong> SHREE — Luxury Indian Couture E-Commerce Platform
<strong>Team:</strong> 3 Members | Frontend · Backend · Database &amp; Cloud</p>
</blockquote>
